ues%2C%20often%20struggling%20with%20a%20gritty%20texture%20or%20an%20unpleasant%2C%20lingering%20whey%20flavor%20on%20the%20back%20end.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENone%20of%20that%20is%20a%20problem%20for%20the%20Starbucks%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20walked%20into%20my%20local%20coffeehouse%20skeptical%20of%20the%20new%20menu%20items%2C%20and%2C%20after%20sampling%20four%20handcrafted%20drinks%20with%20different%20protein%20cold%20foam%20flavors%2C%20left%20thinking%20I%20might%20incorporate%20them%20into%20my%20regular%20rotation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20banana%20foam%20is%20the%20most%20unusual%20of%20the%20bunch.%20When%20paired%20with%20the%20matcha%20latte%2C%20the%20banana%20foam%20works%2C%20and%20it%20may%20have%20been%20my%20favorite.%20The%20chocolate%20and%20sugar-free%20vanilla%20versions%20of%20the%20protein%20foam%20are%20also%20pleasant.%20The%20pumpkin%2C%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstarbucks-pumpkin-spice-season-turnaround-ceo-brian-niccol-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eseasonal%20flavor%3C%2Fa%3E%20staple%20for%20Starbucks%2C%20isn't%20one%20I'd%20return%20to%2C%20though%20I'm%20not%20a%20fan%20of%20the%20flavor%20in%20any%20other%20coffee%20preparation%2C%20either%2C%20so%20I%20can't%20hold%20that%20against%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECEO%20Brian%20Niccol%20said%20during%20the%20company's%20Q3%20earnings%20call%20that%20the%20new%20offerings%20tap%20into%20%26quot%3Bwhat%20has%20become%20one%20of%20our%20most%20popular%20modifiers%20%E2%80%94%20cold%20foam%2C%20which%20grew%2023%25%20year-over-year.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20debuting%20cold%20foam%20as%20a%20topping%20in%202014%2C%20Starbucks%20has%20expanded%20its%20flavor%20options%20to%20include%20offerings%20like%20vanilla%2C%20brown%20sugar%2C%20pumpkin%20spice%2C%20and%20raspberry%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20protein%20variations%20fit%20right%20in%2C%20capitalizing%20on%20a%20trend%20that%20has%20gained%20momentum%20in%20the%20last%20five%20years%2C%20Michael%20Della%20Penna%2C%20chief%20strategy%20officer%20at%20the%20digital%20advertising%20research%20firm%2C%20InMarket%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20in%20July%20following%20the%20announcement%20of%20the%20new%20offerings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Statista%2C%20the%20global%20protein%20market%20is%20estimated%20to%20reach%20over%20%2447.4%20billion%20by%202032%2C%20up%20from%20%2426%20billion%20in%202021.%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported%20that%20protein-enhanced%20products%2C%20including%20sodas%2C%20waters%2C%20powders%2C%20and%20bars%2C%20have%20taken%20over%20the%20aisles%20of%20grocery%20stores.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20protein%20foams%20appeal%20to%20Gen%20Z%20and%20millennials%20in%20particular%2C%20as%20they%20are%20more%20health-conscious%20and%20love%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgen-z-driving-fast-food-beverage-wars-demand-custom-drinks-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecustomizable%2C%20cold%20drinks%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Della%20Penna%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20other%20interesting%20part%20of%20it%20is%20the%20routine%20that%20a%20drink%20like%20that%20can%20create%20for%20a%20consumer%2C%26quot%3B%20Della%20Penna%20said.%20%26quot%3BBy%20introducing%20protein%2C%20that's%20a%20great%20way%20to%20get%20a%20consumer%20back%20as%20they%20move%20about%20their%20daily%20lives%2C%20particularly%20when%20going%20to%20work%20out%20and%20then%20stopping%20to%20get%20a%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fkitchen%2Fhow-to-make-cold-brew-coffee%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ecold%20brew%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20scoop%20of%20protein.%20That%20creates%20that%20sort%20of%20repeatable%20pattern%20of%20visitation%20and%20purchase%20that%20a%20drink%20like%20that%20can%20offer%20to%20a%20segment%20within%20their%20customer%20base.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3