%20majoring%20in%20music%20and%20economics.%20He%20will%20intern%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbcg-head-of-people-ai-core-competencies-performance-evaluations-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EBoston%20Consulting%20Group%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20in%20the%20summer%20of%202026.%20This%20conversation%20has%20been%20condensed%20and%20edited%20for%20clarity.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20I%20started%20college%2C%20I%20never%20thought%20I'd%20end%20up%20in%20consulting.%20I%20was%20a%20music%20major%20playing%20the%20cello%20at%20Brigham%20Young%20University%2C%20and%20consulting%20seemed%20like%20something%20only%20economics%20or%20finance%20students%20did.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20changed%20when%20I%20got%20a%20message%20from%20someone%20in%20BYU's%20Management%20Consulting%20Association%2C%20a%20group%20for%20students%20interested%20in%20consulting.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20I%20was%20serving%20as%20the%20secretary%20of%20the%20Filipino%20Club%2C%20and%20they%20reached%20out%20about%20doing%20a%20cultural%20partnership.%20As%20I%20chatted%20with%20club%20members%2C%20I%20became%20interested%20in%20consulting.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20I%20decided%20to%20apply%20for%20an%20internship%2C%20I%20realized%20I%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20catching%20up%20to%20do.%20I%20didn't%20have%20a%20business%20background%2C%20so%20I%20went%20all-in%20on%20prep%20between%20March%20and%20June%20of%20my%20sophomore%20year%20of%20college.%20I%20used%20RocketBlocks%2C%20a%20platform%20for%20consulting%20and%20tech%20interview%20preparation%2C%20attended%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbain-consulting-tips-for-getting-job-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELeland%20bootcamps%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20even%20hired%20a%20coach.%20All%20in%20all%2C%20I%20probably%20spent%20between%20200%20and%20300%20hours%20preparing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20summer%20of%20this%20year%2C%20soon%20after%20I%20turned%2022%2C%