20bones%20and%20bear%20bile%2C%20and%20the%20inception%20of%20the%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F65156%2Fpangolin-conservation-wildlife-sos%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epangolin%20trafficking%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20attempts%20to%20curb%20illegal%20trade%20of%20the%20species.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20success%20of%20the%20organisation%20masks%20its%20humble%20beginnings.%20But%20Vivek%20Menon%20hasn%E2%80%99t%20forgotten%20these.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20started%20as%20a%20team%20of%20three%20people%20in%20a%20spare%20room%20of%20my%20house.%20Each%20of%20us%20invested%20Rs%205%2C000%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles.%20The%20investment%20was%20secondary.%20Passion%20was%20what%20drove%20WTI%20to%20success.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMenon%20has%20a%20piece%20of%20advice%20that%20he%20believes%20will%20go%20a%20long%20way%20in%20ensuring%20a%20better%20place%20for%20wildlife%2C%20including%20elephants%2C%20on%20the%20planet.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3EFirm%20anti-poaching%20policies%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHaving%20spent%20the%20better%20part%20of%20his%20life%20as%20a%20conservationist%20training%20Indian%20forest%20guards%2C%20rangers%2C%20and%20paramilitary%20forces%20on%20anti-poaching%20activities%20and%20smuggling%20techniques%2C%20Menon%20has%20witnessed%20the%20network%20close%20up.%20But%20he%20insists%20that%2C%20as%20in%20the%20case%20of%20any%20illegal%20activity%2C%20there%20isn%E2%80%99t%20a%20way%20of%20curbing%20it%20completely.%20%E2%80%9COne%20can%20only%20lessen%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20end%2C%20Menon%20says%20the%20forest%20guards%20are%20often%20the%20first%20line%20of%20defence%20to%20stop%20illegal%20trade.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20should%20be%20trained%20in%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F233468%2Findia-tigers-save-vultures-how-to-wildlife-conservation-envir